  "prompt": "What are the best web design firms in New York?",
  "response": "New York City is home to a plethora of top-notch web design firms, each offering unique strengths and specializations. Here are some of the most reputable web design firms in New York, known for their innovative designs, user experience expertise, and client satisfaction:\n\n### 1. **Huge Inc.**\n   - **Specialties:** Digital product design, branding, and user experience.\n   - **Notable Clients:** IKEA, Google, Coca-Cola.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** Huge is known for its ability to create immersive digital experiences that align with their clients' brand identities.\n\n### 2. **R/GA**\n   - **Specialties:** Digital transformation, branding, and marketing.\n   - **Notable Clients:** Nike, Verizon, Google.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** R/GA blends creativity with technology, offering end-to-end solutions that drive business growth.\n\n### 3. **Code and Theory**\n   - **Specialties:** Digital product design, branding, and strategy.\n   - **Notable Clients:** Bank of America, The Washington Post, Maybelline.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** Known for their ability to combine storytelling with technology, Code and Theory create compelling digital experiences.\n\n### 4. **AKQA**\n   - **Specialties:** Innovation, digital strategy, and user experience.\n   - **Notable Clients:** Nike, Audi, Coca-Cola.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** AKQA is celebrated for pushing the boundaries of digital innovation and creating future-forward solutions.\n\n### 5. **Big Spaceship**\n   - **Specialties:** Digital design, branding, and content strategy.\n   - **Notable Clients:** Google, Samsung, Nestle.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** Big Spaceship is known for its collaborative approach and ability to create engaging digital experiences.\n\n### 6. **Firstborn**\n   - **Specialties:** Digital design, branding, and marketing.\n   - **Notable Clients: ** Audi, Samsung, Puma.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** Firstborn combines creativity with technology to deliver impactful digital solutions.\n\n### 7. **Sid Lee**\n   - **Specialties:** Branding, digital design, and advertising.\n   - **Notable Clients:** Adidas, Netflix, Ubisoft.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** Sid Lee is known for its multidisciplinary approach, creating cohesive brand experiences across various platforms.\n\n### 8. **Hush Studios**\n   - **Specialties:** Experiential design, digital installations, and branding.\n   - **Notable Clients:** Google, Sony, Microsoft.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** Hush Studios excels in creating immersive, interactive experiences that captivate audiences.\n\n### 9. **Fantasy Interactive (FI)**\n   - **Specialties:** Digital product design, user experience, and development.\n   - **Notable Clients:** Google, HBO, Netflix.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** FI is known for its ability to create user-centric digital products that are both beautiful and functional.\n\n### 10. **Work & Co**\n   - **Specialties:** Digital product design, branding, and user experience.\n   - **Notable Clients:** Apple, Google, IKEA.\n   - **Why They Stand Out:** Work & Co is celebrated for its hands-on approach and commitment to delivering high-quality digital products.\n\nThese firms are renowned for their ability to create stunning, functional, and user-friendly websites and digital experiences. When choosing the right firm for your needs, consider their portfolio, client reviews, and how their expertise aligns with your project goals.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
